### Generate weighbridge ticket (this validates the exit weighing bridge first before generating the WBT)
POST http://localhost:8190/api/landside/weighbridge-ticket/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "ABC-123",
  "grossWeight": 25000.0,
  "tareWeight": 8000.0,
  "weighingTime": "31/08/2025 15:30"
}

